permute_diag = function(M){
  N = dim(M)[1]
  for (i in 1:N){
    if (i==1){
      opts = M[i,2:N]
      opts = sample(opts)
      M[i,2:N] = opts
    }
    else{
      if (i==N){
        opts = M[i,1:(N-1)]
        opts = sample(opts)
        M[i,1:(N-1)] = opts
      }
      else{
        opts = c(M[i,1:(i-1)],M[i,(i+1):N])
        opts = sample(opts)
        M[i,1:(i-1)] = opts[1:(i-1)]
        M[i,(i+1):N] = opts[i:(N-1)]
      }
    }
  }
  return(M)
}
psocial = permute_diag(social_matrix)
prel_data = rel_data
prel_data$adh_pop = sample(rel_data$adh_pop)
psimilarity = outer(prel_data$adh_pop, prel_data$adh_pop, FUN = "-")
psimilarity  = abs(psimilarity )
psimilarity  = (100 - psimilarity )/100
all = allCorrelations(social_matrix, similarity_matrix, ncomp1=5, ncomp2=5, plot=F)

permute_diag2 = function(M){
  N = dim(M)[1]
  for (i in 1:N){
    opts = M[i,]
    opts = sample(opts)
    M[i, ] = opts
  }
  return(M)
}
